sequenceDiagram
    participant C as RemoteAccessClient
    participant U as User
    participant D as Device
    participant S as RemoteAccessServer
    participant AP as AuthProvider
    participant E as Encryption
    participant FT as FileTransfer
    participant AE as AuditEvent

    U->>C: Launch client, login
    C->>AP: Authenticate via OAuth2/MFA
    AP-->>C: Authentication result
    C->>S: Connect to server
    S->>AP: Verify authentication
    AP-->>S: Auth result
    S->>D: Authorize device
    D-->>S: Device status
    S->>C: Connection established
    C->>S: Request session (start remote desktop)
    S->>E: Encrypt session data
    E-->>S: Encrypted data
    S->>C: Stream remote desktop (encrypted)
    C->>FT: Initiate file transfer
    FT->>E: Encrypt file
    E-->>FT: Encrypted file
    FT->>S: Send file
    S->>AE: Log session event
    AE-->>S: Event logged
    C->>S: End session
    S->>AE: Log session end
    AE-->>S: Event logged
    C->>S: Disconnect
